The campaign posters of former Senate president Dr Abubakar Bukola Saraki for 2023 presidency have surfaced in many parts of Ilorin, the Kwara State capital, Daily Trust has observed. The posters, which were spotted at some strategic places around the capital city, have the logo of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) with the picture of Saraki. Inscriptions such as ‘Sen. Dr. Abubakar Bukola Saraki for President 2023’, ‘Saraki is Back’, ‘Saraki 2023 lets grow Nigeria’ were among the dominant wordings on the campaign posters. Efforts to get the reaction of Saraki’s media aide, Yusuf Olaniyonu, on the issue were not successful as response to calls and text message sent to his phone were still being awaited as at the time of filing this report.